Privacy Policy
We, Soka La Bongo App, are committed to respecting and protecting the privacy of our users. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and disclose information when you use our mobile application, Soka La Bongo, which includes advertising services. By using the Soka La Bongo app, you consent to the practices described in this policy.
Information We Collect
1.1 Personal Information
We do not collect any personally identifiable information (PII) such as your name, address, email address, or phone number directly through the app.
1.2 Non-Personal Information
We may collect non-personal information automatically, such as:
Device Information: We may collect information about your device, including the device type, operating system, unique device identifier, and mobile network information.
Log Data: Our servers automatically record certain information, including your IP address, browser type, app usage, and interactions with advertisements.
Cookies and Similar Technologies: We may use cookies and similar technologies to enhance your app experience and improve our services. These technologies may collect information about your usage patterns and preferences.
Advertisements
2.1 Third-Party Ads
We may display advertisements from third-party ad networks or partners in the Soka La Bongo app. These ads may be tailored based on your interests, app usage, and location.
2.2 Ad Networks
Our app may include advertising from various ad networks. These ad networks may collect and use non-personal information about your interactions with their ads to provide targeted advertisements.
2.3 Data Collected by Ad Networks
Ad networks may collect certain information, including device identifiers, IP addresses, unique application numbers, and other non-personal information. They may use this data to provide personalized ads and measure the effectiveness of their campaigns.
2.4 Opt-Out
You can opt-out of personalized advertisements by adjusting your device settings or using the opt-out mechanisms provided by the ad networks. However, please note that this will not disable all advertisements in the app.
Data Sharing
3.1 Third-Party Service Providers
We may engage third-party service providers to assist us in delivering and analyzing advertisements. These providers may have access to non-personal information collected through the app but are obligated to maintain the confidentiality and security of the data.
3.2 Legal Requirements
We may disclose your information if required by law or in response to a valid legal request, such as a court order or government regulation.
3.3 Business Transfers
In the event of a merger, acquisition, or sale of our company, your information may be transferred as part of the transaction. We will ensure that the recipient of the data complies with this Privacy Policy.
Data Security
We take reasonable measures to protect the information collected through the Soka La Bongo app. However, no data transmission over the internet or mobile network can be guaranteed to be 100% secure. Therefore, we cannot guarantee the absolute security of your information.
Children's Privacy
The Soka La Bongo app is not intended for use by children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If we discover that we have collected such information, we will promptly delete it.
Changes to this Privacy Policy
We reserve the right to update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any material changes by posting the updated policy within the app. Your continued use of the Soka La Bongo app after the changes will signify your acceptance of the revised Privacy Policy.
Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us.
